String[][] ships = new String[] { ship1, ship2 };
```
that you instead write:
```java
private static String[][] ships;
```
and then in your `ships` method, after this line: `String[][] ar = list.toArray(String[][]::new);`, you could write the following:
```java
ships = new String[] {
    new String[] {ar[0][0], ar[1][0]},
